user and personal terms & conditions
and
privacy policy
and I give my consent for processing personal data at SportMember.
I accept to receive relevant digital communication (e-mails/push messages/SMS/WhatsApp) from SportMember. These feature new info, functions, support, and may contain ads from our collaborators and partners.
